					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介", "Junnosuke"},
					"“Seems like all you have to do is stand around to get people to say all sorts of things about you, Touka.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"“我们只是站在一起而已就被人说成这样了啊，桐香。”",
